  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Economic Justice Campaign Launch</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">On June 1, 2011 Oxfam will launch a global campaign on Food Justice in a resource - constrained world. The goal of this campaign is to support people living in poverty to claim power in the way the world manages land; water and climate change so that they can grow or buy enough food to eat now and in the future.   In Nigeria the Voices for food security Campaign will participate in launching of this new campaign with a series of events and activities to introduce the new campaign to the public. The campaign partners will use this opportunity to promote the campaign objectives and priorities using new campaign strategies and tools.</narrative>
  </description>
